Slugslinger smiled behind the flaring Caliburst. How could he be so
lucky, did Havotron know they were fighting rookies? This was going to
be an easy way to notch his belt. He let out a sick cackle with Tremor,
as he walked towards Jet V, "Can you believe it, they sent rookies to
fight us." he said in astonishment. One of his eyes narrowed as he aimed
his gun down into Jet V's face. "Looks like you won't make the big
100000 Autobrat." he said disgustingly. Just before he could pull the
trigger however, an engine roared behind him, and Cliffjumper rammed
into his midback at a smooth 200 mph, causing SLugslinger to crumple up
forward, and fire randomly into the air.
